				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">These suck cash spots confuse me, here's true money:
<br />

<br />
Grab a cleric friend to duo(or shammy, no druid, h8 dr00ids) and head to PoJ. You can run through the Trial of Flame. Trial of Flame is 4 fire based mobs (Imps or fire eles) start off on sides of the room and head towards the center, they have low aggro, if any, ranges if a named spawns kill it  if not say return and do it again, loot is great the named Imp drops a suck helmet and a FT1 mask and occasionly a spec, the named elemental drops Mask of Witness and Ornate Scepter(bout 5k and 15k on 7th) plus occasional specs. During the trial a fire based dot(maybe curse) takes off about 250hp a tick and does around 3kdamage or so, this can be cured with clerix/shammy clense AA or just heals. Even with 300+FR the dot hits 90percent of the time, add the dot and the DPS from the mob pet can go down pretty fast, so I used Rathe's Son and virtue or whatever else buffs could get, mobs are level 60 and give about 1-2percent AA a pop. 
<br />

<br />
Works well on all servers, except 7th hammer,  <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="Wink" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Goodluck.
<br />

<br />
Edit: CotAM works here... trial mob follows you to the prep room  <img src="images/smiles/icon_twisted.gif" alt="Twisted Evil" border="0" /> 
<br />

